\b0 Annuity calculations can be simplified by using an interest table. Table A-4 \b Future Value of Annuity\b0  The value of an annuity is founding by multiplying the annuity with an appropriate multiplier called the \b future value interest factor for an annuity (FVIFA) \b0 which expresses the value at the end of a given number of periods of an annuity of Sh.1 per period invested at a stated interest rate.\par
The future value of an annuity (PMT) can be found by,\par
\trowd\trgaph108\trleft-108\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3
