From the above example,\par
FVA\sub 5 \nosupersub =100,000\'d7FVIFA\sub 12%, 5 years\nosupersub\par
\pard\ltrpar\nowidctlpar\sl360\slmult1\tx3000\b          =100,000\'d76.35280\par
